-- Amplats CEO says restructuring plan will cost $256 million
-- 
-- Fri May 10, 2013 6:43am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/05/10/us-amplats-costs-idUSBRE9490E620130510

 

 JOHANNESBURG  (Reuters) - Anglo American Platinum ( AMSJ.J ) chief executive Chris Griffith said on Friday the costs of the company's new restucturing plan would come to 2.3 billion rand ($256 million). 
 ($1 = 8.9894 South African rand) (Reporting by  Ed Stoddard )